  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to neon</title>

    <para>
      <application>neon</application> is an HTTP and WebDAV
      client library, with a C interface.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
